org.apache.flex.compiler.codegen.js

Interface IJSEmitter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASEmitter, IEmitter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IJSAMDEmitter, IJSFlexJSEmitter, IJSGoogEmitter, IJSVF2JSEmitter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JSAMDEmitter, JSCJSEmitter, JSEmitter, JSFlexJSEmitter, JSGoogEmitter, JSVF2JSEmitter

    public interface IJSEmitter
extends IASEmitter
    The IJSEmitter interface allows abstraction between the IASNodeStrategy and the current output buffer Writer.
    Author:
    Michael Schmalle
